{
  "stem": "13251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, they just moved right in and took over Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This didn't happen right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I-- I remember the frustration of first stopping, which is-- and then nothing happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'd just sit, and sit, and sit, which seemed like forever-- and getting kind of stressed out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why are we not moving?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then slowly, we heard the noise of oncoming commotion, of-- of voices.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then what it was, it was the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the civilians were lined in the street like a parade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were not cheering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were screaming and crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I saw, eventually, the German military coming in their vehicles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the-- the motorcycles with the sidecars, with the shining helmets, and the smiling Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was-- there was the contrast between the-- them smiling and the-- the civilians who were screaming and crying, and you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- I remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was kind of significant-- and of course, then, the-- the trucks, the open trucks with the German soldiers on top.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- so that was why we had to wait all that time, I guess-- because of the congestion that that was causing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we were going to Prague the same time they were going to Prague.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we were on the way to Prague, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So whatever day they took Prague, that's the day I left my parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly that day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All they-- all she said was-- my father was in the background, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't have recollection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she had said, do you sure you want to go?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I remember her asking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we said, sure, why not?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, why-- why the fuss?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why is she crying?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Probably nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is there to take?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
